attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay
Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Terrific opportunity for a modern condo in South Boston under $500K. This sunny loft style unit at the Foundry lives larger than its square footage and has no wasted space.  This unit features a modern kitchen with white shaker cabinets, quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances.  The living space easily accommodates both living and dining. Directly off of the living space is the sleeping area which easily accommodates a queen sized bed and has a sliding barn door for separation from the living area.  The bathroom features a full sized tub, vanity and newly tiled floors.  The building amenities include common laundry, elevator, bike storage and a very reasonable condo fee which includes heat and hot water.   Additional unit features include exposed brick, oversized windows,  central heat and A/C and a bonus loft space for storage.  Conveniently located near West Broadway with shops, restaurants, MBTA and all that South Boston has to offer.  City living at its best!
